name: NADY-PRO SOUND QH-200 NADY STUDIO STEREO

reviews.name: Nady QH-200 Centerstage Studio Stereo Headphones
reviews.reviewText:
I bought these headphones for monitoring of audio recordings and needed a pair of
inexpensive closed backed headphones to block out background noise. These fit the bill at a phenomenal price. Light weight unit with very good sound quality. I highly recommend them for audio recordings.
reviews.title: Inexpensive headphones

reviews.name: Nady QH-200 Centerstage Studio Stereo Headphones
reviews.reviewText: These headphones are excellent for the price. Not studio sound quality, but very agreeable. Could fit a little more comfortably, but acceptable. Overall, I am very pleased.
reviews.title: Nady Studio Stereo Headphones

reviews.name: Nady QH-200 Centerstage Studio Stereo Headphones
reviews.reviewText: These head phones are defiantly you get what you pay for. They didn't work right from the box.
reviews.title: Dont buy

reviews.name: Nady QH-200 Centerstage Studio Stereo Headphones
reviews.reviewText:
I personally did not try this product, our students used it as a prop for a dance performance. Also, this product was chosen because it was oversized and looked excellent on stage.

IT WORKED GREAT FOR WHAT WE PURCHASED IT FOR!
reviews.title: GREAT FOR STAGE PROP
